{"lastModified":1775067042038,"uri":"c::28226710116::vessel::955ebf80-8f22-11f0-b888-fb91e332886d","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Nassau, The Bahamas, Miami, Florida, USA\n\nThe Sunreef Supreme 68 Power BLUE is a unique charter yacht that combines striking design, cutting-edge technology, and outstanding comfort. Built for both adventure and elegance, this fast and stable power catamaran delivers the perfect blend of performance and luxury. Powered by twin Volvo IPS engines, BLUE offers smooth, agile cruising with excellent speed, while her dynamic positioning system ensures effortless maneuvering even in the busiest marinas.\n\nWith over 3,200 sq ft of interior deck space, life on board is designed for both relaxation and entertainment. The expansive bow terrace features oversized sunbeds, a Jacuzzi, and a wide awning for shade, while the flybridge provides two fully equipped bars, multiple lounging areas, and stylish dining spaces. Inside, the yacht’s bright, custom interior includes 4 spacious cabins (master suites and guest bedrooms), each equipped with quartz-finished bathrooms. The full-beam main deck saloon and galley are finished in elegant grey and cream tones with bold accents. Unique among yachts of her size, BLUE also boasts a superyacht-style tender garage and vast living areas, making her a one-of-a-kind choice for an exceptional Miami or Bahamas yacht charter.","blueprint":{"name":"BLUE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::955ebf80-8f22-11f0-b888-fb91e332886d::assets::d41e2870-8f2a-11f0-8c9d-0ff68274ff9a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::955ebf80-8f22-11f0-b888-fb91e332886d::assets::d433ac40-8f2a-11f0-a2a4-8b42f067a5c0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::955ebf80-8f22-11f0-b888-fb91e332886d::assets::d4377cd0-8f2a-11f0-a2a4-8b42f067a5c0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::955ebf80-8f22-11f0-b888-fb91e332886d::assets::d41eebc0-8f2a-11f0-a2a3-8b42f067a5c0/